        <abstract> 
<p>CD’s great interest in JS’s work on fertility of <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi> crosses.</p>  
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Passiflora</hi> trials.</p> 
            <p>"By no means modify even in slightest degree any result."</p> 
<p>CD wishes he had counted rather than weighed <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi> seeds.</p> 
        </abstract>
